      "span_text": "Although in every session the designer proved to be very helpful in steering the conversation, making sketches, mappings and clustering ideas, the designer themselves were not positioned as an expert with unique knowledge (Schuman, 1993) , instead, we emphasised how the co-creation process itself generates unique insights [CITATION_1] ."
